in "Stanley and Livingstone" (1939); Richard Carlson, Deborah Kerr, Stewart 
Granger in "King Solomon's Mines" (1950), and John Huston directing Sean 
Connery, Michael Caine in "The Man Who Would Be King" (1975). 
</P>
